### 1. Physics & Realistic Simulation (The #1 Make-or-Break for “Great”)
**Current State**: `@physics` (rigid bodies, basic collisions, gravity), `@cloth` (soft-body fabric), `@particle_system`, `@flocking`.

**Needed Upgrades**:
- Full **MLS-MPM / SPH / PIC / FLIP fluid simulation** trait (`@fluid` + `@liquid` + `@gas`) with WebGPU compute shaders for splashes, rivers, smoke, fire, blood.
- Advanced soft-body + tearing / fracture (`@soft_body_pro` + `@destruction`).
- Deformable terrain, erosion, wind-driven sand/snow, cloth tearing, muscle/skin deformation.
- Coupled physics (cloth + fluid + rigid + destruction in one scene).
- GPGPU-accelerated crowd simulation (10k+ agents with realistic collision avoidance).

**Priority**: ★★★★★ High  
**Effort**: 4–6 weeks (Rust + WebGPU compute)  
**Impact**: Turns Hololand from “floaty demo” into “feels real” — the single biggest upgrade.

### 2. Rendering & Visual Fidelity
**Current State**: WebGPU + Three.js PBR, `@weather`, basic procedural geometry.

**Needed Upgrades**:
- Volumetric rendering (clouds, god rays, fire/smoke, subsurface scattering for skin/organs).
- Screen-space / hybrid ray-tracing approximations (reflections, GI, shadows) via WebGPU.
- Procedural world generation v2 (`@procedural_worlds` + biome system with erosion/vegetation).
- Dynamic day-night + weather that affects physics (wet surfaces, wind force).
- High-quality avatar skin / clothing / hair (subsurface + strand-based).

**Priority**: ★★★★☆ High  
**Effort**: 3–5 weeks  
**Impact**: Makes worlds photoreal enough for people to want to live in them.

### 3. Persistence & World State
**Current State**: Session-only scenes; basic save/export.

**Needed Upgrades**:
- Persistent world database (CRDT + lightweight server sync layer).
- Auto-save player modifications, inventory, built structures.
- Time-progression system (worlds evolve when offline — plants grow, erosion happens).
- Server-side “world host” mode (optional, cheap Fly.io/Railway tier).

**Priority**: ★★★★★ High  
**Effort**: 2–4 weeks (existing MCP can be extended)  
**Impact**: Hololand feels alive 24/7 instead of resetting every time you leave.

